SIMPLE: pacifier
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pacifier
<hw>Pac"i*fi`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who or that which pacifies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A small device, usually of rubber or plastic
containing a protruding nipple-shaped portion which a baby may place in
its mouth and suck on; -- it is used to keep babies contented.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pacifism</ent>⟦br⟧
